README for IO::Automatic 0.02

=head1 NAME

IO::Automatic - automatically choose a suitable IO::* module

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  use IO::Automatic;

  # scalar
  my $scalar;
  my $io = IO::Automatic->new( \$scalar );
  print $io "Hello World\n";


=head1 DEPENDENCIES

This module has external dependencies on the following modules:

 IO::File
 IO::Scalar
 IO::Zlib
 Module::Build
 Test::More

=head1 INSTALLATION

 perl Build.PL
 perl Build test

and if all goes well

 perl Build install

=head1 HISTORY

What changed over the last 3 revisions

=over

=item 0.02 Sunday 2th January, 2003

	Add IO::Zlib use


=item 0.01 Monday 17th November, 2003

	Initial release
=back

